(i don’t really know how to call this but i guess they’re the main ingredients 😅)

it’s still reaaally hot today so i wanted to have something fresh, this salad is perfect and it’s a nice change from a classic salad! 🥰

-all you have to do is dice all the following into really small pieces: 2 red peppers, 2 yellow peppers, half a cucumber and 1 small red onion. 
-add some pomegranate seeds, the juice of a lemon and the zest, 1tbsp of olive oil, a bit of agave syrup, fresh mint and a pinch of salt.
-mix everything well! 

🇫🇷PREPARATION 
-coupez en petits dés: 2 poivrons rouges, 2 poivrons jaunes, 1/2 concombre et 1 petit oignon rouge.
-ajoutez des grains de grenade, le jus d’un citron et son zeste, une càs d’huile d’olive, un peu de sirop d’agave, de la menthe fraîche et une pincée de sel. 
-mélangez bien et déguster! 🍋

